The paper proposes a new method for dimension reduction and classification, which is a common topic in machine learning and data analysis. The use of Partial Least Squares (PLS) and Principal Component Analysis (PCA) also suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), statistics (cs.ST), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
